gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 118, Lakers 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Lakes, 118-111. Anthony Edwards led Minnesota with 27 points, seven rebounds, and five assists as Karl-Anthony Towns (21 points, six rebounds, four assists) and Rudy Gobert (15 points, 13 rebounds) totaled 36 points. Anthony Davis led the Lakers with 31 points, eight rebounds, four assists, and three blocks while Austin Reaves added 20 points, seven rebounds, and five assists.
